messageBody:
Okay, I have finished about 80% of all the letters. In order to see what
they look like, download all the files at my sourceforge project at:

http://quikscript.sourceforge.net/quikscript-snapshot.tar.gz

If you unpack the files (which most browsers do automatically), you will
find a Readme, and this explains where everything is.

Thanks for your feedback.

Paul
